 & =\Gamma_{ij}^{k}\frac{\partial\vec{R}}{\partial u^{k}}\cdot\frac{\partial\vec{R}}{\partial u^{l}}+\underbrace{L_{ij}\hat{n}\cdot\frac{\vec{R}}{\partial u^{l}}}_{\textnormal{perpendicular}}\\
