\frac{\partial\vec{R}}{\partial v}\cdot\frac{\partial\vec{R}}{\partial u} & \frac{\partial\vec{R}}{\partial v}\cdot\frac{\partial\vec{R}}{\partial v}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}1 & 0\\
