-c^{2} & =\frac{E^{2}}{m_{0}^{2}c^{2}}\left(1-\frac{2GM}{c^{2}r}\right)^{-1}-\left(1-\frac{2MG}{c^{2}r}\right)^{-1}\frac{dr}{d\tau}\frac{dr}{d\tau}\\
